<lb n="0478b08" ed="T"/>大仙、二熟大仙、黑二熟大仙、採清大仙、<note n="0478007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝呼【元】【明】</note><note n="0478007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乎【大】，呼【元】【明】</note><app n="0478007"><lem wit="【大】">乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】 【明】">呼</rdg></app>
