<lb n="0478c05" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT19p0478c0501">「陀訶<note place="inline"><note n="0478018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text"><g ref="#CB03530"/>＝伐【三】</note><note n="0478018" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><g ref="#CB03530"/>【大】，伐【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0478018"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB03530"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【明】">伐</rdg></app>留反</note>陀訶陀訶陀訶陀訶陀訶陀訶陀訶
