<lb n="0478c25" ed="T"/>月賢、日愛、曇<note n="0478026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">德杜＝得杜【宋】，備社【元】【明】</note><note n="0478026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">德杜【大】，得杜【宋】，備社【元】【明】</note><app n="0478026"><lem wit="【大】">德杜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">得杜</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】 【明】">備社</rdg></app>、曇<note n="0478027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">德＝備【元】【明】</note><note n="0478027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">德【大】，備【元】【明】</note><app n="0478027"><lem wit="【大】">德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】 【明】">備</rdg></app>、毘蠅<note place="inline">姚登反</note>
